node.text:
Spent the week here in Minnesota building the track for round two of the championship. Amazing working with @andrewcarlson15 and crew. The track has so much elevation change, huge banks and zer-gravity drops. It’s windy and going to race really well. Almost no dust and great dirt here but we are intentionally not watering a few of the corners to see if the swept line could be a potential solution for other tracks where the soil blue grooves right away. Happy to get some laps on the CanAm to confirm the jumps are super smooth and will be easy on the cars.
@scott_speed @nitrocircus @yokohamatire @redbullmotorsports

node.text:
Behind every good result is a great team. And after every crash the entire @vermont.sportscar crew give up their weekends to work around the clock making sure @rhianongelsomino and I have a car for the next event. Big thanks to @shauniej10 @longshotbrando @seth_alarie and @jamesgilbert for tearing the car down last Sunday and the entire fab shop (the crew in this picture) @Fivestartintvt Angus Newton @Bennyjamescs @tlaplant802 and Nate Eastman for getting the cage fixed and ready for the next phase in under a week. I truly appreciate you guys. Thanks for getting it done. Let’s go win this championship!
@subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @kuhl @motul @dirtfishrally

node.text:
Throwback Thursday to 1995. 11 years old racing at @lorettalynnmx national championship. Its not easy to qualify for this event.. but to all those who made it, congratulations and good luck this week!
@racerxonline #throwbackthursday

node.text:
Some rad highlights from @subarumotorsportsusa at the fastest and most high flying event in the @ara_rally championship. The @newenglandforestrally was hard fought and amazing while it lasted for kblock43 and myself. @brandonsemenuk made it onto the podium in 2nd and moved @subaru_usa into 1st and 2nd halfway through the championship!
@yokohamatire @dirtfishrally @ara_rally @kmcwheels @motul @kuhl @rhianongelsomino @alpinestars @bellhelmets @nitrocircus

node.text: Had fun. Epic event. Wish I could have brought it home. Huge thanks to the crew and @rhianongelsomino for all the work and getting us to the lead. @subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @kmcwheels @dirtfishrally @nitrocircus @kuhl @justlive @pit_viper @motul @ara_rally

node.text:
Fun day. Epic fast stages with big jumps. Off to a rocky start but check out some highlights (lowlights) from the first stage of today. Top 5 drivers within 30 seconds after a wild day one of the @ara_rally championship here at @newenglandforestrally . Going to be an all out charge from all of us tomorrow! 
1 - @mckennamotorsport / @leonjordan1987 
2 - @kblock43 / @alexgelsomino 
3 - @davidhiggins75 / @craigdrew75 
4 - me / @rhianongelsomino 
5 - @brandonsemenuk / @john55sp 
@subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @kmcwheels @kuhl @motul @dirtfishrally

node.text:
Tire changing practice.. like a NASCAR pit stop but completely different 😂 @newenglandforestrally is known for its high attrition rate. Lots of “gotcha’s” and big rocks on the sides of the roads as well as big jumps like @rallyfinland so @rhianongelsomino and I figured it was worth doing a few changes. The @officialwrc drivers will do this in about 1:15 from buckled in to buckled back in.. we took about 1:45 🤦 With the @yokohamatire ‘s and new @kmcwheels we don’t expect to be changing a tire mid stage.. but still worth the practice.
@subarumotorsportsusa @redbullmotorsports

@subarumotorsportsusa @redbullmotorsports @yokohamatire @kmcwheels @kuhl @brandonsemenuk @rhianongelsomino @john55sp @robbie.durant (sorry about your back 👍 glad it healed up!) thanks for stepping up @gregdrally @nitrocircus

Who’s ready for the first full season of @nitrorallycross 🙋 Some clips from the first test at @erxmotorpark (round 2 of the championship). Tickets on sale now. Link in bio.

Sept 24/25 Utah Motorsports Campus – Salt Lake City, UT.

Oct 2/3 ERX Motor Park – Minneapolis, MN.

Nov 13/14 Wild Horse Pass Motorsports Park – Phoenix, AZ.

Nov 20/21 Glen Helen Raceway – San Bernadino, CA.

Dec 4/5 The FIRM – Jacksonville, FL.

@yokohamatire @kmcwheels @subarumotorsportsusa @nitrocircus @alpinestars @bellhelmets @kuhl @motul @redbullmotorsports #carsthatfly #tracksthatthrill

node.text: Always wanted to drive a pro 4 truck. Very similar driving style to my @nitrorallycross Subaru which makes the transition seamless. The truck reacts a bit slower because of the weight and suspension but has the power to make up for it. I will be joining @andrewcarlson15 ‘s @redbullmotorsports @yokohamatire team for @crandonoffroad this year in the Pro-4 class. Only got 5 laps of practice.. but that is 5 more than I got last year before showing up at the World Championships in the pro-2 and I’m much more at home with the aggressive driving style of all wheel drive! #kidinacandystore @redbull @alpinestars @carlsonmoto #gameon
